nsecutive balls of the same color. The `dfs` function explores all possible ways to insert balls from the hand into the board and keeps track of the minimum number of balls needed to clear the board. The `Counter` from the `collections` module is used to efficiently manage the count of balls in the hand.", "estimated_date": 1438905600000}